{"tid":2337512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（始皇帝死而地分）天空大火球墜落中国","createTime":"2020-12-23T10:36:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T16:23:43.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8e15b8c21140a9f4bd3e38cb00ce51635b771841","tid":2337512,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T10:36:06.000Z","msg":"中國今（23）日驚見1顆大火球劃破天際，1架從陝西飛往西藏的航班乘客用手機拍攝過程，而中國公安也已經證實此事，並表示事發當下大地震動，一度以為是發生地震，目前正在搜索是否有落到地上的隕石。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/12/23/phpajXjzi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F12%2F23%2FphpajXjzi.jpg&h=513b0f93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n青海囊謙縣民拍到大火球墜落瞬間。（圖取自微博）<br />\n<br />\n根據中國官媒《新京報》報導，今日有許多中國網友拍到大火球砸向中國領土，當時天尚未破曉的天際瞬間亮得如同白晝，火球在空中發出耀眼的白光，最後明顯碎化並往地面掉落，中國科普媒體《果殼網》主筆虞駿認為，畫面中是1顆火流星，且可能有不少隕石碎塊會落到地面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/12/23/phpfTr368.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F12%2F23%2FphpfTr368.jpg&h=5148954b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n許多中國民眾都目擊大火球。（圖取自微博）<br />\n<br />\n根據中國《瀟湘晨報》報導，該顆大火球出現的具體位置是在青海省囊謙縣，時間為今天清晨時分，當地監視器也拍到大火球從天空劃過，並且閃爍著刺眼的光芒，囊謙公安局回應稱，警方也看到了飛行物，當時大地震動，一度以為是發生地震，但後來才知道原來是大火球引發的震動。<br />\n<br />\n根據中國《封面新聞》報導，囊謙公安局指出，大火球朝南邊飛去，但目前未在該縣南方搜索到相關殘骸。不少中國網友認為「天有異象」，紛紛留言指出「嗯，有意思，天兆」、「許願2021大家都平安順利」、「費勁月球取土，直接給你送貨上門」、「我就搞不明白為啥還不上熱搜」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3390110\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3390110&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp8FcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=c0e4ea9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3390110&h=39a18349\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3390110</a>"},{"pid":"1d87ce64af0d42e57df0207455063401105addbe","tid":2337512,"uid":301050,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:04:25.000Z","msg":"屌咁小事<br />\n中國都未撚爆"},{"pid":"3016efccfabeb96156900cebb73c7f80436be5ba","tid":2337512,"uid":272669,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:06:52.000Z","msg":"都唔係三峽/中南海，準D啦"},{"pid":"067066ec097c0216f44648c3593cb66553619933","tid":2337512,"uid":370061,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:08:34.000Z","msg":"西北<br />\n稱王只宜在秦州"},{"pid":"997c2646fb9f5a39eec7a15dce3bf9cc89b42fcb","tid":2337512,"uid":49853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:08:46.000Z","msg":"麥加登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6558bc55a1fd2e27652f44e3ee6a4642219ed4","tid":2337512,"uid":355748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:15:39.000Z","msg":"四十五象有個太陽<br />\n9up"},{"pid":"f571002b3d23c4280bfc1cc2ef0e8f9efa534ff0","tid":2337512,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:16:41.000Z","msg":"炸撚死咗維尼先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"facc8cfaad51132db5c37ca620bc9c87b83d82e6","tid":2337512,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:19:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKF7LKDW.gif&amp;h=29a1b7da&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"20b262f13d1f259b382ce369ae209248c147086b","tid":2337512,"uid":35860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:31:24.000Z","msg":"月神5號？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db0fb2e2e33aadb0420823cad2ce75365e19d8e","tid":2337512,"uid":74361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y7fptZE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy7fptZE.gif&h=42b12b7a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8264aa05d70122793220c92380628f13397357b4","tid":2337512,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T16:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}